data.description: What a fantastic opportunity for anyone looking for a cozy yet modern place to call home in Freeport Village. With brand new appliances, granite countertops, and fresh paint, it's evident that this home has been well cared for and updated with modern amenities. Plus, it's convenient location near shopping, schools, and other amenities adds to its appeal. It seems like a place where anyone would be excited to settle in and make their own memories. You definitely want to schedule a showing today!
